00:11:37.295 --> 00:11:38.170
BRANDON WALKIN: Yeah.

00:11:38.170 --> 00:11:41.770
Well, the first time I
started using Quartz Composer

00:11:41.770 --> 00:11:45.930
was actually when Mike
Maddess joined Facebook.

00:11:45.930 --> 00:11:48.530
