00:19:12.940 --> 00:19:14.980
You can't dictate what
your user's going to do.

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:18.340
They might reverse the order in
which they move their finger.

00:19:18.340 --> 00:19:20.790
You're not going to
know that ahead of time.

00:19:20.790 --> 00:19:24.630
ADAM DEBRECZENI: Yeah, one of
the big things in Form is we

00:19:24.630 --> 00:19:27.170
were debating this internally
