00:19:34.660 --> 00:19:38.040
is really important when you're
trying to think of new ideas,

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:40.950
because if you conceive of
an idea in After Effects,

00:19:40.950 --> 00:19:43.710
and you load it on your phone,
