00:19:45.485 --> 00:19:47.200
that you give to the engineer.

00:19:47.200 --> 00:19:50.350
Versus a system
that works exactly

00:19:50.350 --> 00:19:53.730
like it would in production--
lets you actually

00:19:53.730 --> 00:19:57.200
tweak little variables
as you're using it.

00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:59.310
So we have this
silly thing where

00:19:59.310 --> 00:20:01.290
if you're dragging
around an image,

00:20:01.290 --> 00:20:04.440
