the spring friction when

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:05.750
you're dragging the image.

00:20:05.750 --> 00:20:07.540
Or you could have
like three iPhones,

00:20:07.540 --> 00:20:10.026
and they could all have
people interacting with it

00:20:10.026 --> 00:20:11.400
with different
amount of springs.

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:14.040
It's really difficult to
fine tune stuff like that

00:20:14.040 --> 00:20:16.262
when it's a pre-baked movie.

00:20:16.262 --> 00:20:16.970
NOAH LEVIN: Yeah.

00:20:16.970 --> 00:20:18.520
That's a really point.

00:20:18.520 --> 00:20:21.950
I'm wondering, though, how
