00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:11.850
can build anything
in Quartz Composer.

00:21:11.850 --> 00:21:14.580
Like it's completely unbounded,
and I think that's important,

00:21:14.580 --> 00:21:17.430
because when you're
trying to be creative,

00:21:17.430 --> 00:21:20.450
and you actually might
want to do something

00:21:20.450 --> 00:21:23.720
that the maker of the
tool hadn't thought about.

00:21:23.720 --> 00:21:30.320
And if you can't get those ideas
out there, it's a huge problem.

00:21:30.320 --> 00:21:31.830
So I do think there
are definitely

00:21:31.830 --> 00:21:34.600
huge problems to the
