00:21:34.600 --> 00:21:37.060
It's intimidating.

00:21:37.060 --> 00:21:40.280
A lot of people
find it confusing.

00:21:40.280 --> 00:21:44.299
And yeah, there are a bunch of
other issues as well, but yeah.

00:21:44.299 --> 00:21:46.090
So I think if I were
to start from scratch,

00:21:46.090 --> 00:21:47.716
it would look way different.

00:21:47.716 --> 00:21:49.340
But it would still
have that capability

00:21:49.340 --> 00:21:52.096
to let people build anything
that they can imagine.

00:21:52.096 --> 00:21:54.470
NOAH LEVIN: I think there's
