00:36:03.690 --> 00:36:07.080
in the desktop probably in the
incumbent tool set, Photoshop,

00:36:07.080 --> 00:36:08.280
Sketch.

00:36:08.280 --> 00:36:10.610
But I think that the
process of bringing that

00:36:10.610 --> 00:36:15.460
to life and kind of
moving that through time

00:36:15.460 --> 00:36:17.810
in an interactive way,
which really prototyping

00:36:17.810 --> 00:36:19.530
is just a storytelling
tool, but I

00:36:19.530 --> 00:36:21.787
see that converging
in one place.

